data.value: The Intel Core i9 12700K 12th Gen Gaming Desktop PC is built for gamers. At its heart is the Intel Core i9 12700K 12th Gen Raptor Lake Processor, providing the power needed for high-end gaming and multitasking. This system is supported by the MSI PRO Z790-S WiFi DDR5 ATX motherboard, ensuring reliable connectivity and support for the latest generation of components. The Corsair VENGEANCE RGB 16GB DDR5 6000MHz CL30 Desktop RAM offers high-speed performance and vibrant aesthetics, making it ideal for gaming and creative tasks. Housed in the Corsair 3000D RGB AIRFLOW Mid-Tower ATX Casing, the PC benefits from excellent airflow and a sleek design.RTX 4070 super with top notch gaming support.
